User Story 1:
As a user, I want to retrieve a list of all available pets in the store

User Story 2:
As a user, I want to retrieve information about a specific pet

User Story 3:
As a user, I want to add a new pet to the store

User Story 4:
As a user, I want to update an existing pet's information

User Story 5:
As a user, I want to delete a pet from the store
